I don't know why but I really enjoy watching these crazy scenarios people find themselves in. Its def interesting. And Billy, is just adorable! He's a cute, funny, sweet young guy, and v professional with his clients too. I used to do the whole rock n roll style myself back in the 80's so I find that cute as well :) The whole Bretherton crew seems to be a nice & likable family. I'll keep watching
